  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/6da1c83259d991fc9938bf8612aedd15.avif?t=1713494663\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br><i>Enter the world of Midnight of Despair, where every step is a test of your skill, patience, and determination. There are no shortcuts here – you'll need to finish in one go, no saving allowed. But fear not, because the journey is just as important as the destination, and every leap forward brings you closer to victory.</i><br><br><br><strong><strong>Gameplay</strong></strong><br><br>Simple yet challenging, Midnight of Despair is all about running, jumping, and timing your moves just right. Each section presents new obstacles and challenges that will push your skills to the limit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/7707c8360dd427767c5d334e37f63472.poster.avif?t=1713494663\" width=590 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/7707c8360dd427767c5d334e37f63472.webm?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/7707c8360dd427767c5d334e37f63472.mp4?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Dash mechanics</strong><br><br>When a regular jump won't cut it, it's time to dash. Master this mechanic to traverse gaps, evade hazards, and reach new heights. With practice, you'll become a master of the dash, soaring through map with precision and grace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/29f646d5fed924f72eb1e4f1471ad037.poster.avif?t=1713494663\" width=590 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/29f646d5fed924f72eb1e4f1471ad037.webm?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/29f646d5fed924f72eb1e4f1471ad037.mp4?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Checkpoints</strong><br><br>As you journey through the game, you'll encounter various characters in need of assistance. Help them out, and they'll reward you with valuable respawn points. These checkpoints are your lifeline, giving you a second chance when things get tough.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/3ad9d056787a597d4b0620361a326e9f.poster.avif?t=1713494663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/3ad9d056787a597d4b0620361a326e9f.webm?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/3ad9d056787a597d4b0620361a326e9f.mp4?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engaging dash mechanics add depth to the gameplay<br></li><li>High level of difficulty ensures a challenge for even the most seasoned players<br></li><li>Engaging map filled with diverse obstacles and challenges<br></li><li>Original soundtrack sets the mood and enhances the overall experience</li></ul><br>Are you ready to face the Midnight of Despair and emerge victorious? Strap in, sharpen your reflexes, and prepare for an adventure unlike any other.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/6da1c83259d991fc9938bf8612aedd15.avif?t=1713494663\" width=616 height=352 /></span><br><br><i>Enter the world of Midnight of Despair, where every step is a test of your skill, patience, and determination. There are no shortcuts here – you'll need to finish in one go, no saving allowed. But fear not, because the journey is just as important as the destination, and every leap forward brings you closer to victory.</i><br><br><br><strong><strong>Gameplay</strong></strong><br><br>Simple yet challenging, Midnight of Despair is all about running, jumping, and timing your moves just right. Each section presents new obstacles and challenges that will push your skills to the limit.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/7707c8360dd427767c5d334e37f63472.poster.avif?t=1713494663\" width=590 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/7707c8360dd427767c5d334e37f63472.webm?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/7707c8360dd427767c5d334e37f63472.mp4?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Dash mechanics</strong><br><br>When a regular jump won't cut it, it's time to dash. Master this mechanic to traverse gaps, evade hazards, and reach new heights. With practice, you'll become a master of the dash, soaring through map with precision and grace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/29f646d5fed924f72eb1e4f1471ad037.poster.avif?t=1713494663\" width=590 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/29f646d5fed924f72eb1e4f1471ad037.webm?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/29f646d5fed924f72eb1e4f1471ad037.mp4?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Checkpoints</strong><br><br>As you journey through the game, you'll encounter various characters in need of assistance. Help them out, and they'll reward you with valuable respawn points. These checkpoints are your lifeline, giving you a second chance when things get tough.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/3ad9d056787a597d4b0620361a326e9f.poster.avif?t=1713494663\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/3ad9d056787a597d4b0620361a326e9f.webm?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2732870/extras/3ad9d056787a597d4b0620361a326e9f.mp4?t=1713494663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Engaging dash mechanics add depth to the gameplay<br></li><li>High level of difficulty ensures a challenge for even the most seasoned players<br></li><li>Engaging map filled with diverse obstacles and challenges<br></li><li>Original soundtrack sets the mood and enhances the overall experience</li></ul><br>Are you ready to face the Midnight of Despair and emerge victorious? Strap in, sharpen your reflexes, and prepare for an adventure unlike any other.",
